Bkind%255D%3Dretainer%26invoice%255Bretainer_id%255D%3D1234\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://subdomain.harvestapp.com/invoices/new?invoice%5Bclient_id%5D=5678\u0026amp;invoice%5Bkind%5D=retainer\u0026amp;invoice%5Bretainer_id%5D=1234\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere \u003cu\u003e5678\u003c/u\u003e needs to be a valid client id for account \u003cstrong\u003eB\u003c/strong\u003e. Then simply fill out the invoice form and save it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eNow in account \u003cstrong\u003eA\u003c/strong\u003e go to \u003ccode\u003ehttps://[SUBDOMAIN].harvestapp.com/retainers/1234\u003c/code\u003e and you will see that the invoice from account \u003cstrong\u003eB\u003c/strong\u003e was added to this retainer.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n","bounty_amount":"500.0","formatted_bounty":"$500","weakness":{"id":75,"name":"Privilege Escalation"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2016-10-29T16:11:30.228Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-131459254.26635212,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":21,"voters":["michiel","bogdantcaciuc","spam404","yaworsk","flashdisk","bugdiscloseguys","gamliel","madrobot","th3g3nt3lman","ak1t4","and 11 more..."],"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"can_edit_custom_fields_attributes":false,"activities":[{"id":1182274,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugTriaged","message":"Hi Edgar,\n\nThanks for this one! I just confirmed the issue and I'm moving it to triage.\nWe will contact you as soon as it is fixed.\n\nCheers,\nJorge","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eHi Edgar,\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThanks for this one! I just confirmed the issue and I\u0026#39;m moving it to triage.\u003cbr\u003e\